  "detailed_description": "Street Fighting Simulator - This is a dynamic fighting game with a side view. You have six levels and eleven characters to choose from. The goal of the game is always the same - you must get to the end of the level and destroy everyone who gets in your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Epic combat system: arm kick, leg kick, block, sprawl kick. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/76031b77478bd3c4307fe3a751dc68e8.poster.avif?t=1717283224\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/76031b77478bd3c4307fe3a751dc68e8.webm?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/76031b77478bd3c4307fe3a751dc68e8.mp4?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Atmospheric locations: garages, courtyard, disco in the style of the eighties, hospital. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/1a78991cd648146641f298a8bb7424c0.poster.avif?t=1717283224\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/1a78991cd648146641f298a8bb7424c0.webm?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/1a78991cd648146641f298a8bb7424c0.mp4?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Training level: here you can learn basic moves and pray to the holy capybara.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/959aad7f3d4e5f6e90e24447614191e3.poster.avif?t=1717283224\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/959aad7f3d4e5f6e90e24447614191e3.webm?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/959aad7f3d4e5f6e90e24447614191e3.mp4?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Street Fighting Simulator - This is a dynamic fighting game with a side view. You have six levels and eleven characters to choose from. The goal of the game is always the same - you must get to the end of the level and destroy everyone who gets in your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Epic combat system: arm kick, leg kick, block, sprawl kick. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/76031b77478bd3c4307fe3a751dc68e8.poster.avif?t=1717283224\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/76031b77478bd3c4307fe3a751dc68e8.webm?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/76031b77478bd3c4307fe3a751dc68e8.mp4?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Atmospheric locations: garages, courtyard, disco in the style of the eighties, hospital. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/1a78991cd648146641f298a8bb7424c0.poster.avif?t=1717283224\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/1a78991cd648146641f298a8bb7424c0.webm?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2835060/extras/1a78991cd648146641f298a8bb7424c0.mp4?t=1717283224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> Training level: here you can learn basic moves and pray to the holy capybara.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com